title: GG - Giant on the Box sample
description:
Two songs from the the Gentle Giant "Giant on the Box" DVD

These songs are from German TV 1974.
Gentle Giant aren&#039;t the most accessible music. The have been called the Kings of Quirk, and the genre is prog rock, art rock or, in the case of GG, baroque-and-roll. I just call it awesome!

Special attention is to be paid to John Weathers, hard hitting drummer extraordinaire.

Now go out and buy that DVD.
